Kita dibawa ke jalan buntu. Lihat petanya.

701
01:06:36,586 --> 01:06:37,837
Petamu salah.

702
01:06:41,258 --> 01:06:42,175
Ada jalan sempit.

703
01:06:48,348 --> 01:06:49,516
Di mana?

704
01:07:02,195 --> 01:07:03,446
031, kiri.

705
01:07:06,199 --> 01:07:08,785
070.

706
01:07:11,412 --> 01:07:12,330
Sekarang.

707
01:07:12,413 --> 01:07:15,458
- Cikar kiri, 070.
- 070.

708
01:07:49,742 --> 01:07:52,328
- Tak terlihat ada jalan.
- Tak bisa lewat.

709
01:07:53,245 --> 01:07:56,582
Kita akan menabrak dinding.
Putar balik, Kapten.

710
01:07:56,665 --> 01:07:59,418
Wadan, jika tak sanggup, diamlah.

711
01:08:15,017 --> 01:08:15,892
Tunggu.

712
