Baik, Kapten. Menunggu perintah.

717
01:09:29,715 --> 01:09:30,967
Wadan pegang kemudi.

718
01:09:47,858 --> 01:09:51,654
Nah. Kita masuk, jemput Presiden Rusia,

719
01:09:51,737 --> 01:09:55,950
berenang, lalu berkumpul
dengan kapal selam AS.

720
01:09:56,033 --> 01:09:58,202
- Itu saja.
- Kedengarannya mudah, Bos.

721
01:09:58,285 --> 01:10:01,080
- Ya.
- Martinelli bagaimana?

722
01:10:03,332 --> 01:10:06,960
Saat selesai dan aku masih hidup,
aku akan menjemputnya.

723
01:10:10,881 --> 01:10:13,175
Kita masuk ke area kudeta, ya?

724
01:10:16,970 --> 01:10:20,682
Jangan tanya aku. Aku buta politik.

725
01:10:22,434 --> 01:10:23,477
Mari berenang.

726
01:11:52,606 --> 01:11:54,775
Tenang, Kawan. Tenang.

727
01:12:00,864 --> 01:12:03,075
- Siapa kalian?
- Tim penyelamat.

728
01:12:03,158 --> 01:12:05,994
Tak resmi. Tiga tentara hantu.

729
01:12:08,872 --> 01:12:11,333
- Kenapa di sini?
- Kau yang lebih tahu.

730
01:12:13,877 --> 01:12:17,339
Kami bisa selamatkan presidenmu
jika kami tahu lokasinya.

731
01:12:19,174 --> 01:12:20,300
Beberapa jam lagi,

732
01:12:21,468 --> 01:12:24,429
angkatan laut kita bentrok
dan situasi memburuk.

733
01:12:26,681 --> 01:12:29,184
Dua rekan kami tak bisa meneruskan.

734
01:12:30,268 --> 01:12:31,937
Semua bergantung pada kami.

735
01:12:37,526 --> 01:12:38,818
Kalian bisa kuantar.

736
01:12:45,033 --> 01:12:46,076
Rawat dia.

737
01:13:16,397 --> 01:13:18,816
Pak Menteri, armada menunggu perintah.

738
01:14:03,527 --> 01:14:04,403
Di sana.

739
01:14:26,758 --> 01:14:27,801
Awas ledakan.

740
01:14:36,434 --> 01:14:37,561
Berdirikan dia!

741
01:14:47,278 --> 01:14:50,949
- Ulurkan tanganmu, Pak.
- Ulurkan tanganmu.

742
01:14:57,163 --> 01:14:59,123
- Tahan!
- Dia orang Amerika?

743
01:14:59,207 --> 01:15:01,626
- Dia membebaskan kita.
- Aku juga enggan, Pak.

744
01:15:01,709 --> 01:15:02,710
Ayo, cepat!

745
01:15:07,799 --> 01:15:08,758
Ada yang tertembak!

746
01:15:10,343 --> 01:15:11,678
Ada yang tertembak!

747
01:15:12,261 --> 01:15:13,262
Lindungi aku!

748
01:15:25,441 --> 01:15:27,568
- Aman!
- Ikuti aku!

749
01:15:27,652 --> 01:15:28,736
Ayo! Ikuti aku!

750
01:15:29,362 --> 01:15:30,238
Oleg!

751
01:15:32,698 --> 01:15:34,784
- Ayo!
- Ayo!

752
01:15:37,161 --> 01:15:38,996
- Tunggu di situ, Pak.
- Hall!

753
01:16:00,059 --> 01:16:01,518
Di pinggir, Pak.

754
01:16:18,327 --> 01:16:19,411
Ayo, Pak!

755
01:16:39,347 --> 01:16:41,433
- Pinjam senjata, Prajurit.
- Sial.

756
01:16:43,226 --> 01:16:44,102
Kita harus pergi.

757
01:16:47,063 --> 01:16:48,064
Persetan kalian.

758
01:16:55,822 --> 01:16:57,031
Johnstone!

759
01:17:04,122 --> 01:17:05,290
Maju!

760
01:17:06,874 --> 01:17:07,834
Cepat!

761
01:17:14,465 --> 01:17:16,426
Ayo! Tidak!

762
01:17:16,509 --> 01:17:19,679
Sialan, Hall! Hall, ayo!

763
01:17:23,808 --> 01:17:25,685
Bill... Dia gugur.

764
01:17:30,481 --> 01:17:33,109
- Sialan.
- Mereka datang.

765
01:17:34,485 --> 01:17:35,611
Harus renang. Ayo!

766
01:17:46,330 --> 01:17:49,500
Menurut perintah, 4 orang Amerika
dan 1 warga sipil Rusia.

767
01:17:50,751 --> 01:17:53,379
Kita tak pernah simulasikan situasi ini.

768
01:17:54,004 --> 01:17:56,674
- Dimengerti.
- Baik. Pergilah.

769
01:18:05,140 --> 01:18:07,726
Semua sistem aman. Siap untuk dilepas.

770
01:18:07,810 --> 01:18:10,229
<i>Mystic, ini Kemudi. Kau pegang kendali.</i>

771
01:18:15,734 --> 01:18:18,737
Cepat! Ayo, cepat!

772
01:18:18,820 --> 01:18:20,822
Cepat! Maju!

773
01:18:25,160 --> 01:18:28,121
Ayo! Maju!

774
01:18:44,554 --> 01:18:46,222
Ayo, cepat!

775
01:18:46,306 --> 01:18:48,099
Ayo!

776
01:18:50,018 --> 01:18:51,186
Lompat!

777
01:18:55,106 --> 01:18:56,566
Menunduk!

778
01:18:57,942 --> 01:18:59,777
Tetap menunduk!

779
01:18:59,861 --> 01:19:03,448
- Menunduk!
- Dia tertembak! Dia terluka!

780
01:19:31,434 --> 01:19:32,852
Ayo, cepat!

781
01:19:46,157 --> 01:19:47,908
Ayo!

782
01:20:04,717 --> 01:20:06,969
Lari terus, Pak! Ayo!

783
01:20:09,638 --> 01:20:13,517
Ayo, cepat! Ayo!

784
01:20:23,735 --> 01:20:25,529
Lari terus, Pak Presiden.

785
01:20:29,199 --> 01:20:30,826
- Ayo!
- Ayolah.

786
01:20:35,622 --> 01:20:38,583
- Ayo!
- Di mana kapalnya?

787
01:20:46,883 --> 01:20:48,218
Itu kapalnya!

788
01:20:48,802 --> 01:20:49,886
Ayo, Pak...

789
01:20:51,721 --> 01:20:52,597
Ayo!

790
01:21:02,232 --> 01:21:03,858
Turun. Lewat sini.

791
01:21:13,284 --> 01:21:15,662
Ayo, Johnstone! Lompat!

792
01:21:17,747 --> 01:21:19,248
Tarik napas dalam, Pak.

793
01:21:36,807 --> 01:21:37,975
Tembak!

794
01:22:09,590 --> 01:22:10,758
Terlalu lama.

795
01:22:10,841 --> 01:22:12,843
Dia tak akan datang, Bung.

796
01:22:17,472 --> 01:22:19,850
Sial! Tarik dia!

797
01:22:21,893 --> 01:22:23,437
Ayo, tarik dia!

798
01:22:23,520 --> 01:22:24,980
Ayo, keluarkan dia!

799
01:22:28,066 --> 01:22:29,901
Di mana yang lain?

800
01:22:33,280 --> 01:22:34,781
Tutup pintu! Kita harus pergi!

801
01:22:37,868 --> 01:22:39,369
Kalian yang tutup.

802
01:22:45,584 --> 01:22:46,501
Sial.

803
01:22:50,422 --> 01:22:51,297
Mari kabur!

804
01:23:09,357 --> 01:23:11,943
<i>Menteri Durov, pasukan Amerika itu kabur.</i>

805
01:23:12,443 --> 01:23:14,821
- Presiden?
<i>- Dibawa oleh mereka.</i>

806
01:23:15,488 --> 01:23:18,408
<i>Jika masih hidup,
dia di kapal selam mereka.</i>

807
01:23:24,455 --> 01:23:25,790
Tutup fyordnya!

808
01:23:26,415 --> 01:23:29,001
Tenggelamkan kapal selam Amerika
sebelum mereka kabur!

809
01:23:30,545 --> 01:23:33,673
Kapten, ada suara samar 300 MHz.
Nada berat.

810
01:23:33,756 --> 01:23:36,300
- Kapal lokal?
- Bukan. Suara mesin bantu.

811
01:23:36,384 --> 01:23:37,426
Di permukaan.

812
01:23:43,432 --> 01:23:44,725
Itu kapal perang.

813
01:24:01,825 --> 01:24:05,287
Itu Yevchenko. Kapal perusak.

814
01:24:06,163 --> 01:24:09,374
Aku yang melatih mereka.
Bidikan mereka jitu.

815
01:24:11,585 --> 01:24:13,420
Tekanan terus meningkat.

816
01:24:17,257 --> 01:24:18,884
Makin dalam, bocornya bertambah.

817
01:24:20,761 --> 01:24:22,262
Ada sinyal, tapi lemah!

818
01:24:22,346 --> 01:24:25,807
Atur baringan 031 untuk bertemu Arkansas.

819
01:24:25,891 --> 01:24:28,852
"Ibu", ini "Anak". Pertahankan sinyalnya.

820
01:24:28,935 --> 01:24:32,147
Kedalaman 170. Mendekat.

821
01:24:38,445 --> 01:24:41,990
Kapten, pelabuhan melaporkan
ada kontak di sensor magnet.

822
01:24:42,073 --> 01:24:45,744
Itu dia! Tembakkan mortir roket
ke baringan yang ditentukan.

823
01:24:56,838 --> 01:24:59,674
Tak bisa bertahan. Kita hampir sampai.

824
01:24:59,758 --> 01:25:01,551
<i>Mystic, ini Kemudi. Kami melihatmu.</i>

825
01:25:01,634 --> 01:25:03,636
Pemandangan yang indah.

826
01:25:08,182 --> 01:25:10,435
<i>Mystic, ini Kemudi. Siap untuk bergabung.</i>

827
01:25:10,518 --> 01:25:11,561
Ayo!

828
01:25:21,779 --> 01:25:25,158
"Anak" sampai!
Pasang kunci! Pengeluaran air!

829
01:25:27,827 --> 01:25:29,245
Ayo! Cepatlah!

830
01:25:29,328 --> 01:25:31,163
Cepat! Keluar dari sini! Ayo!

831
01:25:38,713 --> 01:25:40,172
Mortir roket di dekat kita!

832
01:25:40,256 --> 01:25:41,882
Nyalakan alarm! Terus nyalakan!

833
01:25:41,966 --> 01:25:43,968
- Kecepatan maksimal!
- Kecepatan maksimal!

834
01:25:46,804 --> 01:25:48,639
Ayo! Terus!

835
01:25:48,722 --> 01:25:51,642
Persiapan triase. Luka tembak pada pasien.

836
01:25:52,601 --> 01:25:55,062
- 10 detik sejak mortir masuk!
- Mystic terganjal.

837
01:25:55,145 --> 01:25:57,064
- Dia bisa bocor.
- Ledakkan bautnya.

838
01:25:57,147 --> 01:25:58,148
Buang Mystic!

839
01:25:58,232 --> 01:26:01,819
- Membuang Mystic. Siap.
- 15 detik sejak mortir masuk!

840
01:26:04,321 --> 01:26:05,364
Palka terkunci!

841
01:26:07,574 --> 01:26:10,244
- 20 detik sejak mortir masuk!
- Bersiap hadapi benturan!

842
01:26:10,869 --> 01:26:12,079
Bersiap hadapi benturan!

843
01:26:17,835 --> 01:26:19,169
Tunggu...

844
01:26:26,468 --> 01:26:28,387
Pemandu, stabilkan kapal!

845
01:26:52,619 --> 01:26:55,288
Cikar kiri! Kemudi ke haluan 010.

846
01:26:55,372 --> 01:26:58,458
Cikar kiri! Siap, Kapten! 010!

847
01:27:17,018 --> 01:27:18,102
Ada kebocoran!

848
01:27:19,562 --> 01:27:22,190
Panggil semua mekanik! Sekarang juga!

849
01:27:22,273 --> 01:27:23,649
Panggil semua mekanik!

850
01:27:32,450 --> 01:27:36,203
Park, kau tak apa? Berdirilah, Bung.
Kau tak apa.

851
01:27:36,787 --> 01:27:39,081
- Di mana kapal perusak itu?
- Belum terdeteksi.

852
01:27:39,165 --> 01:27:41,292
Semenit lagi gelombang ledak hilang.

853
01:27:41,375 --> 01:27:44,587
- Mereka juga tak bisa dengar kita.
- Mari coba kabur.

854
01:27:44,670 --> 01:27:47,590
- Kecepatan 30 persen, hemat daya.
- Lapor kerusakan.

855
01:27:48,466 --> 01:27:50,926
Kebakaran di panel utama.
Banjir di ruang torpedo.

856
01:27:51,010 --> 01:27:52,469
Ada kebocoran.

857
01:28:00,227 --> 01:28:04,648
Kapten? Mendeteksi kontak. Baringan 221.

858
01:28:04,732 --> 01:28:06,025
Mereka tak dalam.

859
01:28:06,108 --> 01:28:08,652
Kecepatan maksimal! Karamkan kapal itu!

860
01:28:21,456 --> 01:28:22,499
Itu mereka.

861
01:28:25,085 --> 01:28:27,254
Bersiap menukik cepat dan agresif.

862
01:28:34,177 --> 01:28:36,179
Mereka menembak! Torpedo di dalam air!

863
01:28:36,263 --> 01:28:39,099
Kirim pembelok torpedo! Menyelam!
Ke bawah 60 derajat.

864
01:28:39,182 --> 01:28:40,851
Ke bawah 60 derajat. Siap.

865
01:28:45,438 --> 01:28:49,609
- Kedalaman 795!
- Kedalaman 795! Terima kasih, Kapten.

866
01:28:49,693 --> 01:28:50,902
Kontak dengan perusak!

867
01:28:52,445 --> 01:28:55,407
Baringan Yevchenko 021!
Mereka terus mendekat.

868
01:28:55,490 --> 01:29:00,370
Bersiap menembak.
Siapkan torpedo 1 pada baringan 021.

869
01:29:00,453 --> 01:29:02,872
- Bersiap menembak.
- Baringan 021.

870
01:29:02,956 --> 01:29:04,415
- Kapal siap!
- Kalkulasi siap!

871
01:29:04,499 --> 01:29:05,959
Senjata siap!

872
01:29:10,421 --> 01:29:12,924
- Tahan tembakan.
- Ditahan, Kapten.

873
01:29:18,012 --> 01:29:20,890
Masih ada satu torpedo,
baringan 355, terus mendekat!

874
01:29:20,973 --> 01:29:23,601
- Kita akan menabrak dasar laut!
- Mesin utama panas!

875
01:29:23,684 --> 01:29:26,354
- Kapten, balas tembak?
- Kubilang, tahan.

876
01:29:27,146 --> 01:29:30,107
- Kedalaman?
- 150 kaki di bawah kapal.

877
01:29:30,191 --> 01:29:32,568
- Kembali ke kemiringan nol derajat.
- Trim depan.

878
01:29:32,652 --> 01:29:34,570
Kapten, dasar laut sini empuk?

879
01:29:34,654 --> 01:29:36,864
Ya, Kapten. Lumpur.

880
01:29:38,658 --> 01:29:41,077
Terus ke dasar, cepat!

881
01:29:50,169 --> 01:29:52,421
Kita ke dasar laut seperti lele.

882
01:29:52,505 --> 01:29:54,340
100 kaki lagi!

883
01:29:54,423 --> 01:29:55,549
75 kaki!

884
01:29:56,550 --> 01:29:58,510
- 50 kaki!
- Putar balik, kecepatan penuh!

885
01:29:58,594 --> 01:30:00,846
- Bersiap hadapi benturan!
- 25 kaki!

886
01:30:00,930 --> 01:30:03,140
- 15 kaki!
- Matikan mesin!

887
01:30:03,223 --> 01:30:04,892
- Lima kaki!
- Benturan!

888
01:30:17,654 --> 01:30:19,114
Astaga. Aktifkan itu.

889
01:30:19,740 --> 01:30:23,368
IUSS mendeteksi ledakan di dekat Polyarny.

890
01:30:24,536 --> 01:30:25,579
Kapal selamnya karam?

891
01:30:29,207 --> 01:30:31,168
- Tenggelam, tidak?
- Belum tahu, Pak.

892
01:30:31,251 --> 01:30:32,669
Sialan!

893
01:30:32,753 --> 01:30:36,590
Persiapkan armada untuk menyerang.
Status ke DEFCON 1.

894
01:30:37,424 --> 01:30:40,385
Fisk, Presiden akan menghubungi
sekutu NATO.

895
01:30:40,469 --> 01:30:44,639
Dan dia harus menjelaskan
kenapa Zakarin mati di tangan kita!

896
01:30:44,723 --> 01:30:46,725
Paham, tidak, tindakanmu?

897
01:30:46,808 --> 01:30:49,269
Jika sebelumnya Durov
tak didukung seluruh Rusia,

898
01:30:49,352 --> 01:30:51,938
kini dia pasti didukung Rusia dan dunia!

899
01:30:52,480 --> 01:30:57,193
Setahu mereka, kita menculik
Presiden Rusia dan membunuhnya!

900
01:30:59,529 --> 01:31:01,948
Hari ini kau tak cuma memicu perang...

901
01:31:04,242 --> 01:31:05,660
tapi juga kalah perang.

902
01:31:34,230 --> 01:31:36,148
ARMADA ATLANTIK UTARA AS

903
01:31:49,578 --> 01:31:53,123
Menteri, kapal kita sebentar lagi
akan kontak visual dengan pasukan AS.

904
01:31:53,207 --> 01:31:56,210
Bagus. Suruh mereka menyerang.

905
01:31:57,002 --> 01:31:57,962
Siap, Pak.

906
01:32:18,315 --> 01:32:19,650
Apa itu?

907
01:32:19,733 --> 01:32:21,777
Armada Rusia lainnya bergerak.

908
01:32:21,860 --> 01:32:24,154
Mereka merespons pergerakan kita.

909
01:32:24,238 --> 01:32:26,031
Kita memancing mereka perang.

910
01:33:04,360 --> 01:33:06,196
Kami menangkap prajurit AS.

911
01:33:07,363 --> 01:33:08,364
<i>Eksekusi dia.</i>

912
01:33:24,505 --> 01:33:25,548
Kau kembali.

913
01:33:26,048 --> 01:33:27,592
Ya, sekalian latihan.

914
01:33:32,346 --> 01:33:33,931
Hei.

915
01:33:34,599 --> 01:33:37,351
Kau hebat, Nak. Kau hebat.

916
01:33:38,936 --> 01:33:41,230
Bagaimana kalau kita pergi? Ayo!

917
