918
01:34:14,221 --> 01:34:17,224
Baik, periksa fungsi perlengkapan kalian.

919
01:34:17,307 --> 01:34:19,935
- Siap, Kapten.
- Sonar masih aktif.

920
01:34:20,018 --> 01:34:23,981
- Wadan, pegang kemudi.
- Pegang kemudi. Siap, Kapten.

921
01:34:37,327 --> 01:34:38,245
Pak Presiden.

922
01:34:47,629 --> 01:34:50,006
Kapten Andropov bilang kau bisa dipercaya.

923
01:34:57,931 --> 01:34:59,557
Sambungkan aku ke jenderalku.

924
01:35:01,017 --> 01:35:03,478
Jika mereka tahu faktanya,
Durov akan dihentikan.

925
01:35:03,561 --> 01:35:05,021
Aku paham, Pak.

926
01:35:06,189 --> 01:35:10,318
Tapi jika kapal naik ke area komunikasi,
kau tak akan bertahan hidup.

927
01:35:18,284 --> 01:35:20,078
- Laporkan kerusakan.
- Api dipadamkan.

928
01:35:20,161 --> 01:35:22,413
Kebocoran minim, tapi masih ada.

929
01:35:22,497 --> 01:35:24,665
Awak senjata,
laporkan kondisi ruang torpedo,

930
01:35:24,749 --> 01:35:25,917
Parah, Kapten.

931
01:35:26,000 --> 01:35:27,502
- Turun ke sana.
- Siap.

932
01:35:29,086 --> 01:35:31,380
Sial! McCaw laporkan situasinya!

933
01:35:31,464 --> 01:35:34,675
Siap, status 21.
Empat kebocoran, sedang diperbaiki!

934
01:35:34,759 --> 01:35:37,929
Sialan! Baik, kau ke sana.

935
01:35:39,305 --> 01:35:43,142
Mualim I, ini ruang torpedo.
Banjir 60 cm, Kapten.

936
01:35:43,225 --> 01:35:44,477
<i>Tabung satu rusak.</i>

937
01:35:45,436 --> 01:35:47,188
- Siapkan tabung dua.
- Siap!

938
01:35:47,980 --> 01:35:51,984
- Torpedo 4 ke tabung 2. Ayo!
- Baik. Ayo, kau lama!

939
01:35:52,067 --> 01:35:52,943
Cepat!

940
01:35:56,906 --> 01:36:00,826
- Sial! Awak tertimpa!
- Awak tertimpa!

941
01:36:02,828 --> 01:36:05,331
- Ayo!
- Pindahkan! Ayo!

942
01:36:10,252 --> 01:36:11,295
Kapten.

943
01:36:17,259 --> 01:36:19,303
Kapal perusak berbalik
dan mendekat, Kapten.

944
01:36:19,887 --> 01:36:23,098
- Jaraknya?
- Mendekat sangat cepat. Jarak 500 yard.

945
01:36:39,573 --> 01:36:42,117
Kaplan!

946
01:36:42,200 --> 01:36:45,704
Tarik!

947
01:36:49,666 --> 01:36:50,542
Ayo!

948
01:36:51,459 --> 01:36:52,752
Kaplan! Kau tak apa?

949
01:36:58,008 --> 01:37:01,386
- Ini Kapten.
- Ini ruang torpedo! Tabung dua rusak!

950
01:37:01,469 --> 01:37:04,097
- Ada tabung berfungsi?
- Tak ada, Kapten.

951
01:37:04,180 --> 01:37:05,598
<i>Semua tabung rusak.</i>

952
01:37:14,565 --> 01:37:15,608
Kapten...

953
01:37:17,277 --> 01:37:18,152
Kita ditarget.

954
01:37:27,161 --> 01:37:28,621
Kita sasaran empuk.

955
01:37:35,169 --> 01:37:37,463
Kapten, kau melatih awak
di kapal perusak itu?

956
01:37:37,546 --> 01:37:40,049
Ya. Semuanya.

957
01:37:41,092 --> 01:37:43,594
- Kau kenal dekat?
- Sangat dekat.

958
01:37:45,304 --> 01:37:46,514
Mereka loyal kepadamu?

959
01:37:50,184 --> 01:37:51,185
Tentu.

960
01:37:53,771 --> 01:37:54,814
Buktikan.

961
01:39:01,337 --> 01:39:03,715
<i>Aku Kapten Andropov.</i>

962
01:39:03,798 --> 01:39:08,887
<i>Aku berada di kapal selam Amerika,
USS Arkansas</i>

963
01:39:08,970 --> 01:39:11,014
<i>atas keinginanku sendiri.</i>

964
01:39:12,390 --> 01:39:14,142
Tahan tembakan.

965
01:40:07,736 --> 01:40:11,782
- Arkansas masih hidup, Pak.
- Mereka muncul di dekat Yevchenko.

966
01:40:12,866 --> 01:40:14,827
Sedang apa kapten kapal itu?

967
01:40:22,125 --> 01:40:24,503
Luncurkan misil satu ke kapal selam.

968
01:40:25,462 --> 01:40:27,381
Luncurkan misil satu ke kapal selam!

969
01:40:30,842 --> 01:40:32,636
Patuhi perintah!

970
01:40:34,304 --> 01:40:35,430
Tembak!

971
01:40:41,728 --> 01:40:42,771
Sekarang!

972
01:40:43,480 --> 01:40:44,940
Tembak, Sialan!

973
01:40:48,568 --> 01:40:50,195
Dia bukan lagi komandanmu.

974
01:40:52,697 --> 01:40:53,657
Tembak.

975
01:41:01,664 --> 01:41:04,459
Arkansas menghubungi langsung Yevchenko.

976
01:41:05,335 --> 01:41:06,586
<i>Aku presiden kalian.</i>

977
01:41:08,171 --> 01:41:11,007
<i>Aku bicara
dengan kapasitas sebagai Presiden.</i>

978
01:41:12,342 --> 01:41:15,219
<i>Serangan ke kapal Amerika ini...</i>

979
01:41:17,096 --> 01:41:18,264
<i>berarti pengkhianatan.</i>

980
01:41:20,141 --> 01:41:21,851
- Dia hidup.
- Itu alasannya muncul.

981
01:41:21,934 --> 01:41:23,811
Jayne, kabari jenderal Rusia lain.

982
01:41:23,895 --> 01:41:26,022
Aku butuh rekaman audio ini.

983
01:41:29,066 --> 01:41:34,238
Menteri Durov, awakku tak mau
menembak kapal selam Amerika itu.

984
01:41:34,947 --> 01:41:37,033
Baik, Kapten. Biar aku saja.

985
01:41:37,742 --> 01:41:40,745
- Siapkan misil darat ke laut KH35.
- Siap.

986
01:41:51,213 --> 01:41:55,259
Satelit mendeteksi kendaraan
pembawa KH35 bergerak.

987
01:41:55,342 --> 01:41:56,969
Mau menembak armada kita?

988
01:42:05,269 --> 01:42:06,937
Mereka mengincar Arkansas.

989
01:42:07,021 --> 01:42:09,315
Kabari Glass, Rusia menyerang duluan.

990
01:42:10,107 --> 01:42:12,443
Dia diizinkan menembak.

991
01:42:12,526 --> 01:42:16,905
Pak, jika dia menembak di wilayah Rusia,
seluruh alarm Rusia akan aktif.

992
01:42:16,989 --> 01:42:18,657
Bisa picu serangan nuklir.

993
01:42:18,740 --> 01:42:20,784
Jika kapal selam itu karam
dengan Presiden,

994
01:42:20,868 --> 01:42:22,911
hasilnya juga sama.

995
01:42:22,995 --> 01:42:27,249
Kapten. Pesan dari Washington.
Menyambungkan ke kendali.

996
01:42:29,334 --> 01:42:32,212
- Ini Komandan Glass.
- Ini Laksamana Fisk.

997
01:42:32,296 --> 01:42:35,632
Kau diizinkan melindungi Arkansas
dan para awakmu.

998
01:42:35,716 --> 01:42:37,342
Laksamana, aku ingin tahu.

999
01:42:37,426 --> 01:42:38,927
Apa kita dalam perang?

1000
01:42:39,010 --> 01:42:41,430
Sistem misil Rusia siap menembak.

1001
01:42:42,097 --> 01:42:43,056
<i>Laksamana.</i>

1002
01:42:43,640 --> 01:42:47,269
Jika kita menembak duluan di permukaan,
seluruh dunia akan menyaksikan.

1003
01:42:47,352 --> 01:42:52,440
Kapten Glass, aku Charles Donnegan,
Ketua Kepala Staf Gabungan AS.

1004
01:42:53,024 --> 01:42:55,902
Kau menghadapi orang gila.

1005
01:42:56,987 --> 01:42:59,114
<i>Kuizinkan kau menembak!</i>

1006
01:43:02,617 --> 01:43:04,786
Masih ada misil Tomahawk, Kapten.

1007
01:43:10,250 --> 01:43:13,962
- Mualim I, bersiap tempur.
- Bersiap tempur.

1008
01:43:16,422 --> 01:43:20,093
Prosedur peluncuran dilaksanakan, Menteri.
30 detik lagi.

1009
01:43:29,393 --> 01:43:33,105
Siapkan misil 1 dan 2.
Alihkan sasaran, 3-C-24.

1010
01:43:33,189 --> 01:43:36,192
Siap, Kapten. Alihkan 24-A...

1011
01:43:36,275 --> 01:43:40,238
Isi Tomahawk 2-B dan 2-C.
Kalkulasi posisi kapal perang mereka.

1012
01:43:53,626 --> 01:43:57,087
Kapten, kapal selam AS
membuka tabung misil mereka.

1013
01:44:09,183 --> 01:44:11,352
Tomahawk 1 dan 2 siap meluncur.

1014
01:44:23,030 --> 01:44:24,072
Kapten.

1015
01:44:25,616 --> 01:44:28,493
Kau pernah ambil keputusan
seperti ini, Kapten?

1016
01:44:30,078 --> 01:44:31,121
Belum.

1017
01:44:32,914 --> 01:44:33,832
Kapten.

1018
01:44:34,624 --> 01:44:36,001
Durov akan menembakmu.

1019
01:44:37,461 --> 01:44:38,712
Tidak, Pak.

1020
01:44:40,380 --> 01:44:41,757
Dia akan menembakmu.

1021
01:44:55,729 --> 01:44:57,939
Misil sudah aktif dan siap, Pak.

1022
01:44:59,482 --> 01:45:00,483
Tembak!

1023
01:45:07,907 --> 01:45:09,742
Misil ditembakkan dari Polyarny.

1024
01:45:10,660 --> 01:45:12,036
Dia sedang apa?

1025
01:45:12,662 --> 01:45:14,664
Penembakan terdeteksi, 30 detik.

1026
01:45:25,008 --> 01:45:28,261
Penembakan terdeteksi.
15 detik sebelum berbenturan.

1027
01:45:28,344 --> 01:45:30,138
Misil musuh terkunci, Kapten.

1028
01:45:30,221 --> 01:45:32,473
Kapten, tembakan balasan siap.

1029
01:45:36,060 --> 01:45:36,936
Lepas pengaman.

1030
01:45:37,854 --> 01:45:39,146
Pengaman dilepas.

1031
01:45:44,443 --> 01:45:46,988
- Lima detik.
- Kita harus tembak, Kapten!

1032
01:45:48,072 --> 01:45:49,365
Kapten!

1033
01:45:49,448 --> 01:45:50,533
Tiga detik.

1034
01:45:54,036 --> 01:45:56,372
- Sudah tidak sempat!
- Benturan!

1035
01:46:31,782 --> 01:46:32,908
Apa yang terjadi?

1036
01:47:17,201 --> 01:47:19,579
Pak, ada ledakan di wilayah Rusia.

1037
01:47:19,662 --> 01:47:21,414
- Ulah siapa?
- Bukan kita.

1038
01:47:38,055 --> 01:47:40,308
Pusat Komando Polyarny hancur.

1039
01:47:41,892 --> 01:47:43,686
Misil berasal dari Yevchenko.

1040
01:47:45,896 --> 01:47:47,982
Hei, kerja bagus.

1041
01:47:50,026 --> 01:47:51,610
- Kerja bagus.
- Kapten.

1042
01:47:52,903 --> 01:47:53,779
Wadan.

1043
01:47:55,781 --> 01:47:56,949
Nyaris. Kerja bagus.

1044
01:48:17,136 --> 01:48:18,095
Terima kasih.

1045
01:48:19,179 --> 01:48:20,389
Kau tahu dari mana?

1046
01:48:21,849 --> 01:48:22,808
Aku tidak tahu.

1047
01:48:24,393 --> 01:48:25,352
Aku berharap.

1048
01:48:30,440 --> 01:48:32,234
Armada Rusia mundur.

1049
01:48:32,317 --> 01:48:34,236
Mereka mundur. Jayne, ada info apa?

1050
01:48:35,195 --> 01:48:38,699
Armada Rusia menerima perintah
dari Zakarin di Arkansas.

1051
01:48:39,282 --> 01:48:41,701
Dia memerintahkan AU Rusia
mengamankan Polyarny.

1052
01:49:19,948 --> 01:49:22,075
- Sebentar.
- Hati-hati.

1053
01:49:22,659 --> 01:49:23,951
Selamat datang, Pak.

1054
01:49:26,996 --> 01:49:27,872
Kapten.

1055
01:49:28,790 --> 01:49:29,665
Kapten.

1056
01:49:33,085 --> 01:49:34,212
Aku harus bekerja.

1057
01:49:36,672 --> 01:49:37,715
Aku juga.

1058
01:49:38,966 --> 01:49:41,427
Tidak ada kapten lain

1059
01:49:41,969 --> 01:49:43,679
yang bisa bertindak sepertimu,

1060
01:49:43,763 --> 01:49:45,973
baik di Rusia maupun Amerika.

1061
01:49:46,057 --> 01:49:46,974
Ada.

1062
01:49:48,142 --> 01:49:49,060
Di hadapanku.

1063
01:50:43,488 --> 01:50:46,950
- Bawahanmu bagaimana?
- Akan baik saja. Cuma lecet.

1064
01:50:47,033 --> 01:50:49,494
- Joe Glass.
- Bill Beaman.

1065
01:50:50,704 --> 01:50:53,206
Kau orang gila
yang menyelamatkan Presiden Rusia.

1066
01:50:53,290 --> 01:50:54,708
Dan kau orang gila

1067
01:50:54,791 --> 01:50:56,585
yang membawa kapal ini melalui ranjau.

1068
01:50:56,668 --> 01:50:58,545
- Akan banyak pertanyaan.
- Ya.

1069
01:50:59,045 --> 01:51:02,132
Kisah hebat yang tak bisa kita ceritakan
kepada cucu kita.

1070
01:51:05,552 --> 01:51:08,346
Aku ingin tarik napas
sebelum ke bawah laut.

1071
01:51:09,180 --> 01:51:11,349
Kondisi di permukaan sulit ditebak.

1072
01:51:13,351 --> 01:51:14,519
Hampir saja suram.

1073
01:51:16,729 --> 01:51:18,731
Untungnya, ini sore yang cerah.

1074
01:51:20,275 --> 01:51:21,609
Mari kita pergi.

1075
01:51:23,653 --> 01:51:25,405
Pernah naik Hunter Killer?

1076
01:51:25,488 --> 01:51:28,491
Aku tak mau naik itu. Klaustrofobia.

1077
01:51:29,200 --> 01:51:31,786
Kau pasti aman, asalkan kau tak keluar.

1078
01:52:16,080 --> 01:52:28,165
vi p2 1. e u.o rg

